the sample configuration installed by the package:

    diff -u %%PREFIX%%/etc/paperless.conf \
           %%PREFIX%%/etc/paperless.conf.sample

Then merge in changes as required by editing
%%PREFIX%%/etc/paperless.conf.
EOM
}
